==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: lefty
<hw>lefty</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>a person who uses the left
hand with greater skill than the right; a left-handed person.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> lefthander, southpaw.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>a baseball pitcher who throws the ball with the left
hand.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> left-handed pitcher, left-hander,
southpaw.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Leful</ent>⟦br⟧
